Package: ggspark
Type: Package
Title: ggplot2 Functions to Create Tufte Style Sparklines
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-05-09
Author: Marc Bosch i Matas
Maintainer: Marc Bosch i Matas <mboschmatas@gmail.com>
Description: Functions to help with creating sparklines in the style of Edward Tufte. It computes ribbon geoms with the interquartile ranges and points and/or labels at the beginning, end, max, and min points.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Suggests: tinytest, tinysnapshot, rsvg, svglite, ggrepel
Imports: ggplot2
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://github.com/marcboschmatas/ggspark
